{"tid":889324,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV]星期日2130-2215 暗算天機","createTime":"2018-11-04T13:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T16:39:07.000Z","uid":33798,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"acb0818560b3130d3300410eb87a3ea70b53ef95","tid":889324,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCSSksS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCSSksS.jpg&h=fa67ca50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果一早知道市場走向，係咪就可以隻手遮天？<br />\n如果有人發現呢個秘密，會諗辦法對抗，定係狼狽為奸？<br />\n《暗算天機》，一齊鬥智鬥力！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2128446627212776/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FViuTV.hk%2Fvideos%2F2128446627212776%2F&d=Wr2k4cSpxOUQjfIJ1fi7q5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9b909407\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2128446627212776/</a><br />\n-----<br />\n馬大成（布志綸 飾）以臥底探員身份進入兩極調查多時，成功取得軍事電板後回港後被殺。大學教授方戰（沈震軒 飾）被刑正風（郭偉亮 飾）招攬加入兩極，方戰亦因為大學缺乏資源，苦無機會實踐他的「反隨機理論」，為了完整「反隨機系統」模型，便一口答應投身基金行業。方戰成為兩極定量戰略部第四策略基金主管的第一天，竟於同一座大廈重遇舊大學同學兼倉津製藥銷售部主管貝嘉文（吳海昕 飾）&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"828ef1a61c20959630a9758082f70d453352512e","tid":889324,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:30:46.000Z","msg":"無人睇？"},{"pid":"869e5065d27dfb7678848e221865380f36056ee5","tid":889324,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"同大陸合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"60c17dc5f3f61e511e3fb7e54ad937b42bd85061","tid":889324,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed0c69a6384b039bece66dd54e31bd03c9ff042","tid":889324,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply