a61a5037641","tid":889324,"uid":85284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"睇咗第一集<br />\n我覺得好睇過CCTVB嗰啲自家／合拍劇好多<br />\n唔係求其執葯式嵌埋一渣嘢一齊<br />\n至少我見到製作人係有心想做好啲嘢<br />\n畫面，鏡頭，對白有用心度過<br />\n場口接場口推進尚算流暢<br />\nCCTVB 啲劇其中一個死穴就係場口間推進極差<br />\n唔單止唔流暢，而且係突兀<br />\n一係過多無謂嘢，一係冇重點，一係節奏過快／慢<br />\n呢啲係典型交行貨，唔用腦諗<br />\n只係喺之前睇過嘅戲入面嘅片段裡面<br />\n求其揀完一渣橋段，再求其嵌埋一舊就算數<br />\nEric Kwok 啲戲比我想像好<br />\n雖然唔算老練，但尚算自然有風格，至少表情有細節位<br />\n比起好多CCTVB嗰啲演員，講對白時係接近冇表情變化"},{"pid":"01d448173dd6fd6c462b992e70458b3bd82c5350","tid":889324,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ddfe3b33d37af6615294d9751a8d4adc2df3fa","tid":889324,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca3fadf56591257861695a1f4fb6a0ef42c3f38","tid":889324,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢d朋友真係幫倒忙"},{"pid":"379ad7b5715b96a898fb87b5d5dfd40d7000b97c","tid":889324,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"黑木係日本人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b2b853ac14c68d6a5f80d9a75d83a08b53e024","tid":889324,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"379ad7b5715b96a898fb87b5d5dfd40d7000b97c","tid":889324,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"黑木係日本人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"但個 feel 好香港人"},{"pid":"57d23e2252ddd24a9cada4cf39827259be1106ea","tid":889324,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-1